Dev Notes — Drip Studio v2.1 UI/Build Fixes + UX Improvements
1) Build break: PreviewPane.tsx JSX parse error

Symptom

vite build failed with: Expected ":" but found "}" at PreviewPane.tsx:87:20

Root cause

A JSX ternary was missing its : ... else branch inside the body ? ...map(...) block.

Fix

Completed ternary with : null (or replaced with safer conditional rendering).

Files

src/ui/components/PreviewPane.tsx
2) Expand tab crash: Gate accordion editor kills UI

Symptom

Clicking “Expand” on the Gate card crashed the whole UI.

Root cause

AccordionCardEditor.tsx had an invalid function boundary: missing } after applyTextLayout() and an extra stray } later.

Fix

Restored correct braces so the component renders and event handlers don’t explode.

Files

src/ui/components/AccordionCardEditor.tsx
3) Preview only showed 2 lines (Notes missing), needed all 10 lines

Symptom

Preview showed “What hurts today” then jumped to later lines; users expected all 10 lines visible.

Fix

Rendering updated so preview maps over all usable lines (up to 10) and displays them consistently.
Kept alignment per-line (getLineAlign()).

Files

src/ui/components/PreviewPane.tsx
4) Image card: image code should render actual image preview

Symptom

Selecting image + entering codes like A1/A2/A3 didn’t show the image in the preview.

Fix

Image cards now attempt to render an <img> from a known public path (stickers/images folder).
Fallback behavior: if not found, hides the broken image.

Files

src/ui/components/PreviewPane.tsx
src/ui/styles.css (preview image styling)

Notes

Final wiring uses public/stickers/<CODE>.png pattern (example: /stickers/ali-ai1.png).
5) CSS build break: stray brace in styles.css

Symptom

vite build failed: Unexpected } around src/ui/styles.css:259

Fix

Removed the stray standalone } line.

Files

src/ui/styles.css
6) Modal buttons “locked out” (Wallpaper/Templates/Images/Font/etc stopped opening)

Symptom

Header buttons appeared clickable but modals didn’t open / UI felt dead.

Root cause

CSS override forced .modalOverlay to position: relative and low z-index, breaking overlay behavior:
.topBar,.body,.modalOverlay { position: relative; z-index: 1; }

Fix

Removed .modalOverlay from that selector so overlay stays position: fixed and clickable.

Files

src/ui/styles.css
7) “Card 4” keeps reappearing under the canvas

Symptom

On landing, extra blank/placeholder card showed underneath main layout.

Root causes (both occurred at different times)

A default ad1 block was being pushed into gate blocks in store.ts.
Layout preset blocks were returned by reference (shared objects), so later mutations persisted and “resurrected” blocks.

Fixes

Removed the ad1 push from default gate layout.
Deep-cloned layout preset blocks when creating/applying layouts.

Files

src/core/store.ts
8) Bottom-left ad placeholder sizing issues (must match Gate column)

Symptom

Ad placeholder slot width drifted beyond the Gate panel width.

Fix

Standardized slot width via CSS variable (final target was 520px width).
Confirmed height is min(260px, 28vh) so it scales on shorter screens.

Files

src/ui/styles.css

Resulting slot size

Width: 520px
Height: min(260px, 28vh) (typically 260px on desktop)
9) “Glass window” overlay appeared after skin packs — user wanted floating cards

Symptom

Background looked like a glass panel behind the canvas; user wanted “cards floating over background”.

Fix

Removed/neutralized glass overlay styling on floating canvas container (no backdrop-filter, no panel background).

Files

src/ui/styles.css
10) Templates/Blocks previews right-justified and drifting off-page

Symptom

Template selector grid aligned right; selecting caused drift/off-page and UI looked broken.

Fix

Centered preview grids using fixed tile widths and justify-content: center.
Replaced repeat(5, minmax(0, 1fr)) behavior with repeat(auto-fit, TILE_WIDTH) to prevent stretching.

Files

src/ui/styles.css
11) Font modal features: A+/A- placement + functionality regressions

What was requested

Remove A+/A- from inside Gate editor.
Put font size controls in Font modal.
Add numeric size display + slider + preview sentence.
Add B/I/U toggles.
Add card-number dropdown to apply styling per selected card.

What we did

Moved A+/A- controls out of Gate editor into Font modal.
Added per-page and per-card style support (fontSize + text styles).
Noted there were regressions during patch iterations where the controls disappeared; final intent restored the full feature set.

Files involved across iterations

src/ui/App.tsx (Font modal UI + handlers)
src/ui/components/PreviewPane.tsx (apply styles in render)
src/core/types.ts (style fields)
src/ui/styles.css (modal control styling)
12) Wallpaper catalog improvements + automated import workflow (Option A)

Goal

Stop manually editing wallpaperCatalog.ts every time a wallpaper is added.
Keep wallpapers in public/wallpapers/.
Generate stable 5-digit codes for store/checkout.

Solution

Added a generator script that scans public/wallpapers/ and auto-writes:
src/core/wallpaperCatalog.ts (AUTO-GENERATED)
public/wallpapers/WALLPAPER_CODES.txt (name → code → file)
Hooked generator into npm run dev and npm run build.

Files

scripts/generate-wallpaper-catalog.mjs (new)
package.json (adds gen:wallpapers, runs pre dev/build)
src/core/wallpaperCatalog.ts (generated)
public/wallpapers/WALLPAPER_CODES.txt (generated)

Code rules

If filename matches D#### pattern → code becomes 5-digit padded from digits.
Else → fallback to hash5(name) stable hash.
13) Default wallpaper location (where initial background is set)

Clarified

Default studio wallpaper is set in React state in:
src/ui/App.tsx (studioWallpaper state init)
User can override via Wallpaper modal selection afterward.
14) Bottom-left ad slot: render a specific image asset

Request

Render ali-ai1.png from public/stickers/ inside bottom-left wireframe placeholder.

Implementation

App.tsx: ad slot now contains an <img src="/stickers/ali-ai1.png">
CSS ensures it fills the slot nicely (object-fit: cover).

Files

src/ui/App.tsx
src/ui/styles.css
Known “gotchas” / operational notes
Public folder assets (public/wallpapers, public/stickers) cannot be enumerated client-side; the generator approach is correct.
CSS must never override .modalOverlay into non-fixed positioning, or all modal UX collapses again.
Layout presets must always be cloned before use to prevent mutation bugs (phantom card reappears).
If template grids use fr columns, they will stretch and “drift”; keep fixed tile widths + centered grid.
Quick checklist for future changes
✅ If a modal stops opening: search styles.css for .modalOverlay overrides.
✅ If phantom blocks appear: ensure page.blocks isn’t pointing at preset references.
✅ If a wallpaper is added: just drop it into public/wallpapers/, generator handles it.
✅ If image codes change: ensure public/stickers/<CODE>.png exists or update the resolver in PreviewPane.

